Coinbase

USA | Related people:
  • Brian Armstrong (CEO)
Coinbase is a publicly traded company that operates the Coinbase cryptocurrency exchange platform. Its investors have included Union Square Ventures and Andreessen Horowitz. Coinbase also operates the Stand With Crypto advocacy group and PAC, and the Coinbase Innovation PAC corporation PAC.
